1.17
log
@use .Rv; no change of meaning; from Kaspars at Bankovskis dot net
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: msgctl.2,v 1.16 2014/11/15 22:19:53 guenther Exp $
.\"	$NetBSD: msgctl.2,v 1.2 1997/03/27 08:20:35 mikel Exp $
